    "2.11.0": "- Added an archaeology data handler mode (requires 1.20 feature flags to use).\n- Added the ability to change a structure\u0027s biomes in the config.\n\nChangelog:\nhttps://gitlab.com/modding-legacy/structure-gel-api/-/blob/1.19.x/changelogs/1.19.4-v2.11.0.md",
    "2.10.0": "Updated to 1.19.4 with many QoL changes\n\nChangelog:\nhttps://gitlab.com/modding-legacy/structure-gel-api/-/blob/1.19.x/changelogs/1.19.4-v2.10.0.md\n"
  },
  "1.19.3": {
